            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6bT8wH": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Always Ask for a Proper Invoice",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>5. Always Ask for a Proper Invoice</h2>",
            "custom_id": "always",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_hL7nBn": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Always_Ask_for_a_Proper_Invoice.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9erNkQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A genuine purchase always comes with a detailed bill.</p><p>What to look for: Purity, weight, making charges, and HUID mentioned clearly.</p><p>Real-life example: A seller offers a discount but avoids giving a bill. You decline and buy from a store that provides a proper invoice.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Use the BIS Care App",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>6. Use the BIS Care App</h3>",
            "custom_id": "use",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_hmhUEL": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Use_the_BIS_Care_App.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mhKqgW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Technology makes verification easy.</p><p>What to look for: Matching details after entering the HUID number in the app.</p><p>Real-life example: Before leaving the store, you verify your bracelet on the BIS app and confirm its authenticity instantly.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Cc6XPQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "7. Observe the Stamp Placement",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>7. Observe the Stamp Placement</h2>",
            "custom_id": "observe",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_xa6Py6": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Try_a_Basic_Magnet_Test.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ihgCiQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Hallmark stamps are often placed in less visible areas.</p><p>What to look for: Engravings inside rings, near clasps, or behind pendants.</p><p>Real-life example: You can’t see the hallmark on a necklace initially, but upon checking the clasp, you find the marking.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Q8hnff": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "8. Try a Basic Magnet Test",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>8. Try a Basic Magnet Test</h3>",
            "custom_id": "try-a",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TqKPQB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Gold is a non-magnetic metal.</p><p>What to look for: The jewellery should not stick to a magnet.</p><p>Real-life example: At home, you test an old gold bracelet with a magnet. It doesn’t stick, giving you confidence about its authenticity.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_z7bEiV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9. Compare Weight with Market Price",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>9. Compare Weight with Market Price</h3>",
            "custom_id": "compare",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_hMTFz6": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Compare_Weight_with_Market_Price.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Wqd9ti": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Gold prices are standardized based on purity.</p><p>What to look for: Price consistency with current gold rates.</p><p>Real-life example: A seller offers a gold ring at a very low price compared to market rates. You double-check and realise the purity may be compromised.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_KeKqEV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "10. Buy Only from BIS-Certified Jewellers",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>10. Buy Only from BIS-Certified Jewellers</h3>",
            "custom_id": "buy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPXFtW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The safest way to ensure authenticity is to buy from trusted sellers.</p><p>What to look for: BIS certification displayed in-store or mentioned by the jeweller.</p><p>Real-life example: For a wedding purchas</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AtPerk": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Thoughts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Thoughts</h2>",
            "custom_id": "final",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_MWChdj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Verifying gold hallmarking is simple if you know what to check. By paying attention to the BIS logo, purity mark, HUID number, and proper documentation, you can confidently buy authentic gold jewellery.</p><p>Gold is not just an ornament—it’s an investment. A little awareness ensures you get both beauty and value.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
